      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJESTIC ZEAL (1) flew the lids from the middle with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 20.01 when a 0.8 lengths winner over 352m at Q Lakeside. Expected to go well again. FEDERAL EMERAN (3) had the drop on the lead early on but could only manage second, beaten 4 lengths (19.14) at Q Straight in a OPEN over 350m. Has performed well from this box with a win and seven minor placings to her name from 11 starts. Expected to be in the finish again. MARGARET'S ANGEL (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (26.14) in a Grade 5 at Q Lakeside. Cannot be taken lightly. FIVE BIRDIES (4) scored last time and appeals as a top-three prospect.",
